'''開放知識基金會'''（{{Lang-en|Open Knowledge Foundation}}，縮寫：OKF）是一個全球性的非營利網絡，免費推廣和分享信息。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Open Knowledge: About|url=https://okfn.org/about/|accessdate=25 October 2015|work=okfn.org|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001190009/https://okfn.org/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它由路福斯·伯罗科（Rufus Pollock）於2004年5月20日成立，並於2004年5月24日啟動<ref>{{Cite web|title=Open Knowledge Foundation launched|url=http://blog.okfn.org/2004/05/24/open-knowledge-foundation-launched/|accessdate=25 October 2015|date=2004-05-24|work=Open Knowledge Foundation Weblog|archive-date=2011-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001095231/http://blog.okfn.org/2004/05/24/open-knowledge-foundation-launched/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在英國[[劍橋|劍橋]]。該基金會是在[[英格兰|英格蘭]]和[[威爾斯|威爾士]]註冊成立的私人擔保有限公司。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Open Knowledge: About - Legal notice|url=https://okfn.org/about/|accessdate=28 July 2019|work=okfn.org|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001190009/https://okfn.org/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016年5月至2019年5月，該組織改名為「開放知識國際」，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Open Knowledge International – our new name!|url=https://blog.okfn.org/2016/05/23/open-knowledge-international-our-new-name/|date=23 May 2016|access-date=2020-09-03|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226133550/https://blog.okfn.org/2016/05/23/open-knowledge-international-our-new-name/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但在2019年5月決定改回「開放知識基金會」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=For a fair, free and open future: celebrating 15 years of the Open Knowledge Foundation|url=https://blog.okfn.org/2019/05/20/for-a-fair-free-and-open-future-celebrating-15-years-of-the-open-knowledge-foundation/|date=20 May 2019|access-date=2020-09-03|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424191331/https://blog.okfn.org/2019/05/20/for-a-fair-free-and-open-future-celebrating-15-years-of-the-open-knowledge-foundation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

